title: Infernal Man-Thing 01-03 (2012|Digital-TheGroup)
description:
Steve Gerber writes and Kevin Nowlan illustrates this fun limited series about Man-Thing. Promotional info from the collected edition - "It's the story no one thought existed -Steve Gerber's final Man-Thing tale! First, in the classic "Song-Cry of the Living Dead Man," Man-Thing stumbles across a lone man, desperately scribbling down his thoughts in the halls of an abandoned insane asylum. But this man's inner demons appear in the flesh to torment him - and it's driving the Man-Thing mad! Will Brian Lazarus succumb to the madness of everyday life?"

This digital copy of the three individual issues is courtesy of TheGroup. All credit to them, please seed and enjoy! :-)
